ue of the FlashVar.			@usageNote You must first initialize {@link StageReference} before using this class.		*/		public static function getValue(key:String):String {			return Reflect.field(StageReference.getStage().loaderInfo.parameters,key);		}				/**			Checks to if FlashVar exists.						@param key: The name of the FlashVar to check for existence.			@return Returns <code>true</code> if the key exists; otherwise <code>false</code>.			@usageNote You must first initialize {@link StageReference} before using this class.		*/		public static function hasKey(key:String):Bool {			return FlashVarUtil.getValue(key) != null;		}	}
